feedback: The final question of the main task didn't make sense to me.

The phrasing of the last question seemed a bit odd and I didn't quite understand what was being asked. I thought the AI adjusted its responses based on proposer inputs and thus there wasn't a clear "average" amount.
I really couldn't say why the AI made the decisions it did. It would seem like, if the responder was getting the better deal, they would accept more of the time, but I guess the AI didn't think so.
Great instructions, very well laid out and well put together
